## 3.7 Analytical Matrix: Decision Table for Choosing Each Keyword

| Scenario | Use `throw` | Use `throws` | Use `finally` |
|---|---|---|---|
| Custom business rule violation | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Declaring a method may fail | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Closing file/DB connections | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Validating user input manually | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Delegating exception to caller | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Releasing locks/resources | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Converting exception type | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Logging before propagating | ✅ (rethrow) | ❌ | Optional |
