## 5.2 Part B Questions (14 Marks Each)

### Question A [KTU University Exam - Dec 2023]

**Q: (a)** Explain exception handling in Java with its hierarchy. Discuss the use of `throw` and `throws` keywords with examples. **(7 marks)**

**(b)** Write a Java program demonstrating the use of `try`, `catch`, `finally`, and custom exception. **(7 marks)**

