### Question B [KTU University Exam - May 2024]

**Q: (a)** Explain the difference between checked and unchecked exceptions. Give examples. **(7 marks)**

**(b)** Write a Java program that uses `throws` to propagate a `FileNotFoundException` and demonstrate its handling using nested `try-catch-finally` blocks. **(7 marks)**

