- ✅ **Adapter classes** (`MouseAdapter`, `KeyAdapter`, `WindowAdapter`) provide empty implementations to avoid boilerplate code
- ✅ **No adapter exists** for `ActionListener` or `ItemListener` (single-method interfaces)
- ✅ **`e.getSource()`** returns the Object reference of the component that fired the event
