> [!WARNING]
> **Method Signature Trap:** Students often write `addActionListener()` on a `JFrame` or `JLabel`. Only components that extend `AbstractButton` (and `JMenuItem` family) accept `ActionListener`. **2-mark penalty** is common for this mistake in KTU valuation.

