- **Banking software:** "Submit", "Cancel", "Reset" buttons in transaction forms.
- **IDE toolbars:** "Run ▶", "Debug 🐞", "Build 🔨" — every one of these is a `JButton` (or an `AbstractButton` subclass).
- **Embedded HMI panels:** Industrial control dashboards use Swing-based `JButton` widgets in legacy SCADA systems.
